{"tid":1615541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★著名大鱷巴斯：香港經濟嚴重下滑　聯匯制度恐崩潰","createTime":"2019-10-03T06:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:29:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab0129fd227c13350c5327e9074210f9f7ed542","tid":1615541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"香港社會動盪，近年多番揚言沽空港元及人民幣的著名大鱷巴斯(Kyle Bass)預期，香港面臨嚴重的經濟下滑風險，並押注聯繫匯率機制將被打破，主因是社會事件持續升級。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，巴斯周三(2日)在一個會議表示，香港經濟正消耗流動資金，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>預期外匯儲備在9月和10月將惡化，在接下來的12至18個月將有明顯的資金外流，香港經濟已是一個「巨大的問號」</strong></span>。報道指，包括巴斯等交易員認為，香港社會動盪將令資金外逃，推高利率，並迫使香港放棄運行逾30年的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，受美國對中資公司到美上市的審查趨嚴格，巴斯指，他本人將永遠不會投資於內地的網絡巨頭。<br />\n隨着香港近來社會衝突升級，高盛日前發表的報告估計，截至8月份，港元存款流向新加坡的額度高達30億至40億美元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191003/bkn-20191003100151652-1003_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191003%2Fbkn-20191003100151652-1003_00842_001.html&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=068a378d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191003/bkn-20191003100151652-1003_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fd8c15038704ee166ebc48e5c256a98ba0c45b96","tid":1615541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f381149cc2e05f67cf1f1bcf6fc48fbd4093a5f7","tid":1615541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ba87134a7e752ece51f6f5a38cf2fe66f2599c","tid":1615541,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"報捷"},{"pid":"e7391c53dc41408e1b0690df478e1ccd6df54ca7","tid":1615541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ba87134a7e752ece51f6f5a38cf2fe66f2599c","tid":1615541,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"報捷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d7f17816bb9dc2b1c5ec4704a072f5ac33ae9","tid":1615541,"uid":277060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"佢係鄧梓峰定連登巴絲? XD"},{"pid":"e6a882eb837e644163a797619d2f92f0a4a16c24","tid":1615541,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"30億至40億美金存款算唔算多"},{"pid":"1b84fea237735171f4976896a2e24696493c71e7","tid":1615541,"uid":94999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"聯繫匯率會被打破係因為d美金俾支那抽走晒，而唔係因為d咩野社會事件"},{"pid":"95850ed031132fdacdaeba7f5d1184766de7f0d0","tid":1615541,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6a882eb837e644163a797619d2f92f0a4a16c24","tid":1615541,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"30億至40億美金存款算唔算多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"未夠多"},{"pid":"0b9ab007bb71fbd18a4436fe96c5de3b86f25b03","tid":1615541,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"612d7f17816bb9dc2b1c5ec4704a072f5ac33